{"tid":17600,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"林早泄，你開口我就返高登","createTime":"2016-12-02T01:39:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T02:29:10.000Z","uid":22148,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"799d72e2827cd8e6d0a205a90af4d8667aa9cc33","tid":17600,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:39:53.000Z","msg":"林CEO, 你同一眾高登巴打道歉，我深深被打動。<br />\n<br />\n老老豆豆，邊有高高在上嘅CEO同顧客道歉？我未見過！除非個CEO真係做得好錯，引起公憤或被杯葛，繼而導致一班員工飯碗不保。不過，就算係咁，高高在上嘅CEO又點會理一眾網民同員工感受，所以我一直覺得你一定唔會道歉。<br />\n<br />\n點知，你居然公開道歉，我係好感動的！<br />\n<br />\n不過呢，你場外叫人返高登亦唔係太尊重！<br />\n<br />\n一係咁，你入黎留言，再貼一張相，要有賬號+LIHKG做背景，我第一個返高登！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">利申：賬號已封...</span>"},{"pid":"bd68b408796943b4389441444c4b4c0810972495","tid":17600,"uid":33896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:42:32.000Z","msg":"番高登試下開個post屌佢就得<br />\n睇下佢會唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8897c559b970fa20f512d784f9d47854570e9248","tid":17600,"uid":22148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:46:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>番高登試下開個post屌佢就得<br />\n睇下佢會唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無賬號，不了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01caef3d5fc5a46d2ecbd178fcb14a9fe699ca97","tid":17600,"uid":24041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:49:40.000Z","msg":"我話鳩知佢入黎貼張食緊屎既相，我都唔撚番去 <br />\n完全冇留戀，如果番撚左去只會一世比條撚屌食住"},{"pid":"40564da13c3912cdf02f94a5a68d1d933984055b","tid":17